OL,3,CCouncillor dies after collapsing
OL,4,Cduring budget meeting
OL,6,FA North Lincolnshire councillor has
OL,7,Fdied after he was taken ill during a
OL,8,Fspeech in a budget meeting.
OL,10,FCllr Steve Swift collapsed last month
OL,11,Fwhile he was speaking at the meeting
OL,12,Fand was taken to Castle Hill Hospital
OL,13,Ffor specialist treatment.
OL,15,FThe meeting was abandoned and
OL,16,Fadjourned, with the budget instead
OL,17,Fpassed the following week.
