OL,4,Cduring budget meeting
OL,6,FA statement from read: "It is with
OL,7,Fgreat sadness that we learned this
OL,8,Fmorning that Councillor Steve Swift
OL,9,Fhas lost his courageous battle. Cllr
OL,10,FSwift collapsed whilst speaking on
OL,11,Fbehalf of his residents at the full
OL,12,Fcouncil meeting on the 22 February.
OL,14,F"He received immediate emergency first
OL,15,Faid and then first-class treatment
OL,16,Ffrom the paramedics who were quickly
OL,17,Fon scene. He was taken to Castle Hill
OL,18,FHospital where, despite receiving a
OL,19,Fsuperb level of care and support, he
OL,20,Fsadly passed away.
