OL,6,F"Cllr Swift served the people of North
OL,7,FLincolnshire since 1996 and before
OL,8,Fthat he was a Councillor on the
OL,9,FHumberside County Council. He was also
OL,10,Fa former mayor of Bottesford Town
OL,11,FCouncil.
OL,13,F"Known as 'Swifty' to many he was a
OL,14,Ffountain of knowledge, and his memory
OL,15,Fwas legendary. Steve's motivation was
OL,16,Falways local government and serving
OL,17,Fpeople at a local level.
