OL,6,F"For many years he served the people
OL,7,Fof Bottesford and Brumby with a
OL,8,Fpassion that was unsurpassed. He will
OL,9,Fbe sadly missed by everyone who knew
OL,10,Fhim on both a personal and
OL,11,Fprofessional basis."
OL,13,FCllr Swift was re-elected last year to
OL,14,Frepresent Brumby Ward, along with
OL,15,FCllrs Len Foster and Susan Armitage.
